{"word":"φυλάσσω","slug":"φυλάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>φυλάσσω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ assoc.\">assoc.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a> <el>φυλ-</el>formations]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘serve as sentinel’, <b>guard, watch:</b> of shepherds <b><a href='B:490 2:8'>Lk 2:8</a>;</b> of jailers <b><a href='B:490 8:29'>8:29</a>; <a href='B:510 12:4'>Ac 12:4</a>; <a href='B:510 23:35'>23:35</a>; <a href='B:510 28:16'>28:16</a>;</b> of a security contingent <b><a href='B:480 15:25'>Mk 15:25</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘ensure that <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> remains intact’, <b>keep safe, preserve <a href='B:500 12:25'>J 12:25</a>; <a href='B:500 17:12'>17:12</a>; <a href='B:600 3:3'>2 Th 3:3</a>; <a href='B:610 6:20'>1 Ti 6:20</a>; <a href='B:620 1:12'>2 Ti 1:12</a>, <a href='B:620 1:14'>14</a>; <a href='B:680 2:5'>2 Pt 2:5</a>; <a href='B:690 5:21'>1 J 5:21</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 24</a>.</b> Of holding <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> temporarily for someone <b>watch <a href='B:510 22:20'>Ac 22:20</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘be on guard against’ or ‘be on the alert against’, <b>avoid <a href='B:490 12:15'>Lk 12:15</a>; <a href='B:510 21:25'>Ac 21:25</a>; <a href='B:620 4:15'>2 Ti 4:15</a>; <a href='B:680 3:17'>2 Pt 3:17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>4.</pp></b> ‘keep <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> from being violated’, <b>keep, observe <a href='B:470 19:20'>Mt 19:20</a>; <a href='B:490 11:28'>Lk 11:28</a>; <a href='B:500 12:47'>J 12:47</a>; <a href='B:510 7:53'>Ac 7:53</a>; <a href='B:510 16:4'>16:4</a>; <a href='B:510 21:24'>21:24</a>; <a href='B:520 2:26'>Ro 2:26</a>; <a href='B:550 6:13'>Gal 6:13</a>; <a href='B:610 5:21'>1 Ti 5:21</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:φύλαξ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp